{"ja529:0.1":"Jataka ","ja529:0.2":"Satthinipata ","ja529:0.3":"Sonakavagga ","ja529:0.4":"1 Sonakajataka ","ja529:1.1":"“Tassa sutva satam dammi, ","ja529:1.2":"sahassam dittha sonakam; ","ja529:1.3":"Ko me sonakamakkhati, ","ja529:1.4":"sahayam pamsukilitam”. ","ja529:2.1":"“Athabravi manavako, ","ja529:2.2":"daharo pancaculako; ","ja529:2.3":"Mayham sutva satam dehi, ","ja529:2.4":"sahassam dittha sonakam; ","ja529:2.5":"Aham te sonakakkhissam, ","ja529:2.6":"sahayam pamsukilitam”. ","ja529:3.1":"“Katamasmim so janapade, ","ja529:3.2":"ratthesu nigamesu ca; ","ja529:3.3":"Kattha sonakamaddakkhi, ","ja529:3.4":"tam me akkhahi pucchito”. ","ja529:4.1":"“Taveva deva vijite, ","ja529:4.2":"tavevuyyanabhumiya; ","ja529:4.3":"Ujuvamsa mahasala, ","ja529:4.4":"nilobhasa manorama. ","ja529:5.1":"Titthanti meghasamana, ","ja529:5.2":"ramma annonnanissita; ","ja529:5.3":"Tesam mulamhi sonako, ","ja529:5.4":"jhayati anupadano; ","ja529:5.5":"Upadanesu lokesu, ","ja529:5.6":"dayhamanesu nibbuto”. ","ja529:6.1":"Tato ca raja payasi, ","ja529:6.2":"senaya caturangiya; ","ja529:6.3":"Karapetva samam maggam, ","ja529:6.4":"agama yena sonako. ","ja529:7.1":"Uyyanabhumim gantvana, ","ja529:7.2":"vicaranto brahavane; ","ja529:7.3":"Asinam sonakam dakkhi, ","ja529:7.4":"dayhamanesu nibbutam. ","ja529:8.1":"“Kapano vatayam bhikkhu, ","ja529:8.2":"mundo sanghatiparuto; ","ja529:8.3":"Amatiko apitiko, ","ja529:8.4":"rukkhamulasmi jhayati”. ","ja529:9.1":"Imam vakyam nisametva, ","ja529:9.2":"Sonako etadabravi; ","ja529:9.3":"“Na raja kapano hoti, ","ja529:9.4":"Dhammam kayena phassayam. ","ja529:10.1":"Yo ca dhammam nirankatva, ","ja529:10.2":"Adhammamanuvattati; ","ja529:10.3":"Sa raja kapano hoti, ","ja529:10.4":"Papo papaparayano”. ","ja529:11.1":"“Arindamoti me namam, ","ja529:11.2":"kasirajati mam vidu; ","ja529:11.3":"Kacci bhoto sukhasseyya, ","ja529:11.4":"idha pattassa sonaka”. ","ja529:12.1":"“Sadapi bhadramadhanassa, ","ja529:12.2":"Anagarassa bhikkhuno; ","ja529:12.3":"Na tesam kotthe openti, ","ja529:12.4":"Na kumbhim na khalopiyam; ","ja529:12.5":"Paranitthitamesana, ","ja529:12.6":"Tena yapenti subbata. ","ja529:13.1":"Dutiyampi bhadramadhanassa, ","ja529:13.2":"Anagarassa bhikkhuno; ","ja529:13.3":"Anavajjapindo bhottabbo, ","ja529:13.4":"Na ca kocuparodhati. ","ja529:14.1":"Tatiyampi bhadramadhanassa, ","ja529:14.2":"Anagarassa bhikkhuno; ","ja529:14.3":"Nibbuto pindo bhottabbo, ","ja529:14.4":"Na ca kocuparodhati. ","ja529:15.1":"Catutthampi bhadramadhanassa, ","ja529:15.2":"Anagarassa bhikkhuno; ","ja529:15.3":"Muttassa ratthe carato, ","ja529:15.4":"Sango yassa na vijjati. ","ja529:16.1":"Pancamampi bhadramadhanassa, ","ja529:16.2":"Anagarassa bhikkhuno; ","ja529:16.3":"Nagaramhi dayhamanamhi, ","ja529:16.4":"Nassa kinci adayhatha. ","ja529:17.1":"Chatthampi bhadramadhanassa, ","ja529:17.2":"Anagarassa bhikkhuno; ","ja529:17.3":"Ratthe vilumpamanamhi, ","ja529:17.4":"Nassa kinci ahiratha. ","ja529:18.1":"Sattamampi bhadramadhanassa, ","ja529:18.2":"Anagarassa bhikkhuno; ","ja529:18.3":"Corehi rakkhitam maggam, ","ja529:18.4":"Ye canne paripanthika; ","ja529:18.5":"Pattacivaramadaya, ","ja529:18.6":"Sotthim gacchati subbato. ","ja529:19.1":"Atthamampi bhadramadhanassa, ","ja529:19.2":"Anagarassa bhikkhuno; ","ja529:19.3":"Yam yam disam pakkamati, ","ja529:19.4":"Anapekkhova gacchati”. ","ja529:20.1":"“Bahuni samanabhadrani, ","ja529:20.2":"ye tvam bhikkhu pasamsasi; ","ja529:20.3":"Ahanca giddho kamesu, ","ja529:20.4":"katham kahami sonaka. ","ja529:21.1":"Piya me manusa kama, ","ja529:21.2":"atho dibyapi me piya; ","ja529:21.3":"Atha kena nu vannena, ","ja529:21.4":"ubho loke labhamase”. ","ja529:22.1":"“Kame giddha kamarata, ","ja529:22.2":"kamesu adhimucchita; ","ja529:22.3":"Nara papani katvana, ","ja529:22.4":"upapajjanti duggatim. ","ja529:23.1":"Ye ca kame pahantvana, ","ja529:23.2":"nikkhanta akutobhaya; ","ja529:23.3":"Ekodibhavadhigata, ","ja529:23.4":"na te gacchanti duggatim. ","ja529:24.1":"Upamam te karissami, ","ja529:24.2":"tam sunohi arindama; ","ja529:24.3":"Upamaya midhekacce, ","ja529:24.4":"attham jananti pandita. ","ja529:25.1":"Gangaya kunapam disva, ","ja529:25.2":"vuyhamanam mahannave; ","ja529:25.3":"Vayaso samacintesi, ","ja529:25.4":"appapanno acetaso. ","ja529:26.1":"‘Yananca vatidam laddham, ","ja529:26.2":"bhakkho cayam anappako’; ","ja529:26.3":"Tattha rattim tattha diva, ","ja529:26.4":"tattheva nirato mano. ","ja529:27.1":"Khadam nagassa mamsani, ","ja529:27.2":"pivam bhagirathodakam; ","ja529:27.3":"Sampassam vanacetyani, ","ja529:27.4":"na palettha vihangamo. ","ja529:28.1":"Tanca otarani ganga, ","ja529:28.2":"pamattam kunape ratam; ","ja529:28.3":"Samuddam ajjhagahasi, ","ja529:28.4":"agati yattha pakkhinam. ","ja529:29.1":"So ca bhakkhaparikkhino, ","ja529:29.2":"udapatva vihangamo; ","ja529:29.3":"Na pacchato na purato, ","ja529:29.4":"nuttaram nopi dakkhinam. ","ja529:30.1":"Dipam so najjhagaganchi, ","ja529:30.2":"agati yattha pakkhinam; ","ja529:30.3":"So ca tattheva papattha, ","ja529:30.4":"yatha dubbalako tatha. ","ja529:31.1":"Tanca samuddika maccha, ","ja529:31.2":"kumbhila makara susu; ","ja529:31.3":"Pasayhakara khadimsu, ","ja529:31.4":"phandamanam vipakkhakam. ","ja529:32.1":"Evameva tuvam raja, ","ja529:32.2":"ye canne kamabhogino; ","ja529:32.3":"Giddha ce na vamissanti, ","ja529:32.4":"kakapannava te vidu. ","ja529:33.1":"Esa te upama raja, ","ja529:33.2":"atthasandassani kata; ","ja529:33.3":"Tvanca pannayase tena, ","ja529:33.4":"yadi kahasi va na va. ","ja529:34.1":"Ekavacampi dvivacam, ","ja529:34.2":"bhaneyya anukampako; ","ja529:34.3":"Tatuttarim na bhaseyya, ","ja529:34.4":"dasovayyassa santike”. ","ja529:35.1":"Idam vatvana pakkami, ","ja529:35.2":"sonako amitabuddhima; ","ja529:35.3":"Vehase antalikkhasmim, ","ja529:35.4":"anusasitvana khattiyam. ","ja529:36.1":"“Ko nume rajakattaro, ","ja529:36.2":"sudda veyyattamagata; ","ja529:36.3":"Rajjam niyyadayissami, ","ja529:36.4":"naham rajjena matthiko. ","ja529:37.1":"Ajjeva pabbajissami, ","ja529:37.2":"Ko janna maranam suve; ","ja529:37.3":"Maham kakova dummedho, ","ja529:37.4":"Kamanam vasamanvagam”. ","ja529:38.1":"“Atthi te daharo putto, ","ja529:38.2":"dighavu ratthavaddhano; ","ja529:38.3":"Tam rajje abhisincassu, ","ja529:38.4":"so no raja bhavissati”. ","ja529:39.1":"“Khippam kumaramanetha, ","ja529:39.2":"dighavum ratthavaddhanam; ","ja529:39.3":"Tam rajje abhisincissam, ","ja529:39.4":"so vo raja bhavissati”. ","ja529:40.1":"Tato kumaramanesum, ","ja529:40.2":"dighavum ratthavaddhanam; ","ja529:40.3":"Tam disva alapi raja, ","ja529:40.4":"ekaputtam manoramam. ","ja529:41.1":"“Satthi gamasahassani, ","ja529:41.2":"paripunnani sabbaso; ","ja529:41.3":"Te putta patipajjassu, ","ja529:41.4":"rajjam niyyadayami te. ","ja529:42.1":"Ajjeva pabbajissami, ","ja529:42.2":"ko janna maranam suve; ","ja529:42.3":"Maham kakova dummedho, ","ja529:42.4":"kamanam vasamanvagam. ","ja529:43.1":"Satthi nagasahassani, ","ja529:43.2":"sabbalankarabhusita; ","ja529:43.3":"Suvannakaccha matanga, ","ja529:43.4":"hemakappanavasasa. ","ja529:44.1":"Arulha gamaniyehi, ","ja529:44.2":"tomarankusapanibhi; ","ja529:44.3":"Te putta patipajjassu, ","ja529:44.4":"rajjam niyyadayami te. ","ja529:45.1":"Ajjeva pabbajissami, ","ja529:45.2":"ko janna maranam suve; ","ja529:45.3":"Maham kakova dummedho, ","ja529:45.4":"kamanam vasamanvagam. ","ja529:46.1":"Satthi assasahassani, ","ja529:46.2":"sabbalankarabhusita; ","ja529:46.3":"Ajaniyava jatiya, ","ja529:46.4":"sindhava sighavahino. ","ja529:47.1":"Arulha gamaniyehi, ","ja529:47.2":"illiyacapadharibhi; ","ja529:47.3":"Te putta patipajjassu, ","ja529:47.4":"rajjam niyyadayami te. ","ja529:48.1":"Ajjeva pabbajissami, ","ja529:48.2":"ko janna maranam suve; ","ja529:48.3":"Maham kakova dummedho, ","ja529:48.4":"kamanam vasamanvagam. ","ja529:49.1":"Satthi rathasahassani, ","ja529:49.2":"sannaddha ussitaddhaja; ","ja529:49.3":"Dipa athopi veyyaggha, ","ja529:49.4":"sabbalankarabhusita. ","ja529:50.1":"Arulha gamaniyehi, ","ja529:50.2":"capahatthehi vammibhi; ","ja529:50.3":"Te putta patipajjassu, ","ja529:50.4":"rajjam niyyadayami te. ","ja529:51.1":"Ajjeva pabbajissami, ","ja529:51.2":"ko janna maranam suve; ","ja529:51.3":"Maham kakova dummedho, ","ja529:51.4":"kamanam vasamanvagam. ","ja529:52.1":"Satthi dhenusahassani, ","ja529:52.2":"rohanna pungavusabha; ","ja529:52.3":"Ta putta patipajjassu, ","ja529:52.4":"rajjam niyyadayami te. ","ja529:53.1":"Ajjeva pabbajissami, ","ja529:53.2":"ko janna maranam suve; ","ja529:53.3":"Maham kakova dummedho, ","ja529:53.4":"kamanam vasamanvagam. ","ja529:54.1":"Solasitthisahassani, ","ja529:54.2":"sabbalankarabhusita; ","ja529:54.3":"Vicitravatthabharana, ","ja529:54.4":"amuttamanikundala; ","ja529:54.5":"Ta putta patipajjassu, ","ja529:54.6":"rajjam niyyadayami te. ","ja529:55.1":"Ajjeva pabbajissami, ","ja529:55.2":"ko janna maranam suve; ","ja529:55.3":"Maham kakova dummedho, ","ja529:55.4":"kamanam vasamanvagam”. ","ja529:56.1":"“Daharasseva me tata, ","ja529:56.2":"mata matati me sutam; ","ja529:56.3":"Taya vina aham tata, ","ja529:56.4":"jivitumpi na ussahe. ","ja529:57.1":"Yatha arannakam nagam, ","ja529:57.2":"poto anveti pacchato; ","ja529:57.3":"Jessantam giriduggesu, ","ja529:57.4":"samesu visamesu ca. ","ja529:58.1":"Evam tam anugacchami, ","ja529:58.2":"pattamadaya pacchato; ","ja529:58.3":"Subharo te bhavissami, ","ja529:58.4":"na te hessami dubbharo”. ","ja529:59.1":"“Yatha samuddikam navam, ","ja529:59.2":"vanijanam dhanesinam; ","ja529:59.3":"Voharo tattha ganheyya, ","ja529:59.4":"vanija byasani siya. ","ja529:60.1":"Evamevayam puttakali, ","ja529:60.2":"antarayakaro mama; ","ja529:60.3":"Imam kumaram papetha, ","ja529:60.4":"pasadam rativaddhanam. ","ja529:61.1":"Tattha kambusahatthayo, ","ja529:61.2":"yatha sakkamva acchara; ","ja529:61.3":"Ta nam tattha ramessanti, ","ja529:61.4":"tahi ceso ramissati. ","ja529:62.1":"Tato kumaram papesum, ","ja529:62.2":"pasadam rativaddhanam; ","ja529:62.3":"Tam disva avacum kanna, ","ja529:62.4":"dighavum ratthavaddhanam. ","ja529:63.1":"Devata nusi gandhabbo, ","ja529:63.2":"adu sakko purindado; ","ja529:63.3":"Ko va tvam kassa va putto, ","ja529:63.4":"katham janemu tam mayam”. ","ja529:64.1":"“Namhi devo na gandhabbo, ","ja529:64.2":"Napi sakko purindado; ","ja529:64.3":"Kasiranno aham putto, ","ja529:64.4":"Dighavu ratthavaddhano; ","ja529:64.5":"Mamam bharatha bhaddam vo, ","ja529:64.6":"Aham bhatta bhavami vo”. ","ja529:65.1":"Tam tattha avacum kanna, ","ja529:65.2":"dighavum ratthavaddhanam; ","ja529:65.3":"“Kuhim raja anuppatto, ","ja529:65.4":"ito raja kuhim gato”. ","ja529:66.1":"“Pankam raja atikkanto, ","ja529:66.2":"thale raja patitthito; ","ja529:66.3":"Akantakam agahanam, ","ja529:66.4":"patipanno mahapatham. ","ja529:67.1":"Ahanca patipannosmi, ","ja529:67.2":"maggam duggatigaminam; ","ja529:67.3":"Sakantakam sagahanam, ","ja529:67.4":"yena gacchanti duggatim”. ","ja529:68.1":"“Tassa te svagatam raja, ","ja529:68.2":"sihasseva giribbajam; ","ja529:68.3":"Anusasa maharaja, ","ja529:68.4":"tvam no sabbasamissaro”ti. ","ja529:69.1":"Sonakajatakam pathamam. "}